<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Mindfullness | Izhan's Vision</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --color-bg-primary: #0C1B2E;
            --color-bg-secondary: #1A3A5F;
            --color-bg-tertiary: #2A1E3F;
            --color-text-primary: #E2E8F0;
            --color-text-secondary: #A0AEC0;
            --color-accent-primary: #3B82F6;
            --color-accent-secondary: #2563EB;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
                rgba(12,27,46,1), 
                rgba(42,30,63,1)
            );
            color: var(--color-text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 5%;
            background: rgba(12,27,46,0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .navbar-logo {
            color: var(--color-accent-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar-logo span {
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        }

        .navbar-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .navbar-links a {
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-links a:hover {
            color: var(--color-accent-primary);
        }

        .about-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .section {
            background: rgba(42,30,63,0.5);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        h1, h2 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-primary), var(--color-accent-secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        }

        .mission-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .mission-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--color-accent-primary);
            flex: 0 0 100px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .mission-section {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .mission-icon {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/" class="navbar-logo">
            Mindfullness 
            <span>by Izhan</span>
        </a>
        <div class="navbar-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/chat">Chat</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="about-container">
        <h1>About Mindfullness</h1>

        <div class="section mission-section">
            <div class="mission-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Placeholder for mission statement. You can replace this with your specific mission description.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>About the Developer</h2>
            <p>Placeholder for developer background. You can provide details about yourself here.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Technology</h2>
            <p>Placeholder for technology description. Explain the technologies used in Mindfullness.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
